ion service — backend\",\n    \"9. Add evidence-based confidence tiers and integrate calibration into prompts — backend\",\n    \"10. Add targeted query rewriting for RAG — backend\",\n    \"11. Add calibration display and confidence tiers — frontend\",\n    \"12. Add typed workflow orchestration — risk→what-if→recommendation pipeline (backend)\",\n    \"13. Add plan recommendations UI — frontend\"\n  ]\n}\n\nPrevious step 2 (Fix CommitDraftAssistService — Bound historical queries to 12 weeks) has been completed and approved.\nFiles changed in the previous step:\n.pi/duet/runs/2026-03-29T18-32-40-613Z-32faa966/cost.json\n.pi/duet/runs/2026-03-29T18-32-40-613Z-32faa966/observations.jsonl\n.pi/duet/runs/2026-03-29T18-32-40-613Z-32faa966/sessions/continuous/relay-a/2026-03-29T19-04-03-296Z_a136707b-c87b-4208-a6ea-807038373dcb.jsonl\n.pi/duet/runs/2026-03-29T18-32-40-613Z-32faa966/sessions/continuous/relay-b/2026-03-29T19-09-03-837Z_8d227e47-9181-4199-810a-1293e952c4f2.jsonl\n.pi/duet/runs/2026-03-29T18-32-40-613Z-32faa966/state.json\nbackend/src/main/java/com/weeklycommit/ai/service/CommitDraftAssistService.java\nbackend/src/main/java/com/weeklycommit/domain/repository/WeeklyCommitRepository.java\nbackend/src/test/java/com/weeklycommit/ai/service/CommitDraftAssistServiceTest.java\n.pi/duet/runs/2026-03-29T18-32-40-613Z-32faa966/steps/2\n\nYour session has context from prior steps. The repository may have changed since your last turn.\nBefore making assumptions about file contents, verify the current state of any files you need to modify.\nDo NOT re-read files that are unrelated to the current step.\n\nStep 3: Fix CommitLintService — Remove wasted LLM call and fix RiskDetectionService context persistence\n{\n  \"id\": \"step-3\",\n  \"title\": \"Fix CommitLintService — Remove wasted LLM call and fix RiskDetectionService context persistence\",\n  \"description\": \"Fix two bugs: (1) CommitLintService.enrichSoftGuidanceFromAi() calls the LLM but discards the output. (2) R